{"tid":1546624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家駒生日 有無人寫信","createTime":"2019-09-06T10:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T15:49:35.000Z","uid":57073,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f549de6d3ab0e467ba88f83d3316d89ad8ad1e77","tid":1546624,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"【獄中第二個生日】<br />\n<br />\n大家生日的時候，都希望有人會對自己講句生日快樂，身陷港共黑獄的義士也不例外。<br />\n<br />\n2016 年旺角初一警民衝突事件中，被控暴動罪成、判囚 42 個月刑期監禁的黃家駒將於下星期生日，這會是他在陰冷監倉中渡過的第二個生日。另外，家駒與梁天琦和盧健民的上訴，將於10月 9日一同審理。除了希望家駒生日快樂外，本平台亦祝願他上訴得直，公義得到伸張。<br />\n<br />\n由即日起到星期日（9月8日）下午六時止，大家請在本帖文或以私訊聯絡星火同盟 抗爭支援，留下給家駒的祝福語，我們將會收集然後轉送到他手上，陪伴他渡過這個在監牢內孤單的生日。<br />\n<br />\n只要每人多做一步，就可為身陷囹圄的義士送上無限溫暖；一句生日快樂，已可令在囚者感覺不被遺忘。身陷港共黑獄的這段漫長苦日子，需要我們每一個人支持他一起撐過去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2540050536282063&amp;id=1965117443775378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2540050536282063%26id%3D1965117443775378&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=cbde5505\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2540050536282063&amp;id=1965117443775378</a>"},{"pid":"ef3d070bfb0fae115b66c8b6ded5f9824b57b87d","tid":1546624,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=8be2991f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"c24d748b1dee876b65cc395cb73d9682c96a96f4","tid":1546624,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"